videos.description: Markell Johnson drives off the pick and roll then passes to Braxton Beverly who hits the wide open deep 3-pointer to extend NC State's lead.
videos.headline: Beverly's deep three extends NC State lead

videos.description: Allerik Freeman takes the ball from beyond the 3-point line, slips through defenders and gets up for 2 points.
videos.headline: NC State's Freeman elevates for the layup

videos.description: Markell Johnson moves past defenders and finds his teammate Omer Yurtseven who slams it down with ease to extend NC State's lead.
videos.headline: Johnson finds Yurtseven for the slam down

videos.description: With only seconds to go on the shot clock, Dusan Ristic finds Parker Jackson-Cartwright who drains a deep 3-pointer with a second left on the possession.
videos.headline: Arizona's Jackson-Cartwright drains deep last-second three

videos.description: Allonzo Trier drives down the lane and hangs in the air before tossing in the and-1 bucket.
videos.headline: Arizona's Trier lays out for and-1

videos.description: Off of an Arizona missed shot, Allerik Freeman takes the ball from his end of the court, drives, and puts the moves on defenders for two points.
videos.headline: NC State's Freeman hits the flashy layup

videos.description: Brandon Randolph dribbles down the court off the steal and passes to teammate Allonzo Trier who slams it down, bringing Arizona within two points of NC State.
videos.headline: Trier's fast-break dunk helps narrow Arizona's deficit

videos.description: Allerik Freeman drives from well beyond the 3-point line and puts the moves on defenders for the circus-like, and-1 layup.
videos.headline: Freeman makes an acrobatic and-1 layup
